snippet.title: Orange Hat Reviews
snippet.description:
Movies, shows, entertainment review. I report on controversial topics within entertainment venues. I give news on upcoming movies and such. I also give my own thoughts on movies and celebrity life and activity. I do some Rants. I will take some requests. I will engage with viewers if they are civil.

I do Versus Streams every other friday. I do movie discussions every now and then.
